ulous on its own.',NULL,0),(267,1,'Frontera Shiraz','This intense red wine presents aromas of red fruit with a strong, cherry aroma. Shiraz grapes produce a deep, dark, dense wine, with smooth tannins and rich, red fruit flavors.',NULL,0),(268,1,'KWV Shiraz','',NULL,0),(269,1,'Nederburg Shiraz','Ripe berries enhanced by spicy notes of cinnamon and clove.',NULL,0),(270,1,'Simonsig Cabernet Sauvignon/Shiraz','This vibrant, ruby coloured wine shows cheerful notes of red berries layered with luscious plums. A whiff of cinnamon spice contributes to the primary fruit sensation. Youthful yet tame tannins sooth the palate making this wine a true super quaffer.',NULL,0),(271,1,'35 South Reserve Cabernet Sauvignon','Intense ripe red fruit aromas, with cassis and vanilla notes. On the palate a very concentrate wine, with sweet and elegant tannins, and a nice persistent finish.',NULL,0),(272,1,'Boschendal Pavillion Shiraz Cabernet Sauvignon','This wine displays an attractive array of dark red fruit and subtle spice on the nose complemented by light toasty flavours. The palate is well balanced, soft and with a juicy centre, showing the friendly fruity side of a younger Shiraz and the volume from the Cabernet.',NULL,0),(273,1,'Casillero del Diablo Cabernet Sauvignon','It owns an intense cherry and plum bouquet, with vanilla and toast finishes. Is one of the red varieties with full wine in mouth, elegant and ideal to match beef in pepper sauce.',NULL,0),(274,1,'Frontera Cabernet Sauvignon','Bright and intense ruby red color, with violet reflections. Aromas of candied fruits, essences to plums with chocolate notes. Harmonic tannins, medium body, good aftertaste.',NULL,0),(275,1,'Gato Negro Cabernet Merlot','',NULL,0),(276,1,'Gato Negro Cabernet Sauvignon','Dark ruby colour. Very intense Cab, full red fruit aromas, berries, cherry,  cassis perfectly mixed with sweet vanilla and coconuts notes. A fresh mouth feel, medium body, slightly rich, soft tannins and long pleasant finish.',NULL,0),(277,1,'KWV Cabernet Sauvigno','',NULL,0),(278,1,'Namaqua Cabernet Sauvignon','Namaqua Cabernet Sauvignon offers big berry flavours that is rewarding from the very first sniff. Its dark fruity notes of currant and blackberry is complemented with a velvety finish that´ll leave a lush, lasting impression.',NULL,0),(279,1,'Nederburg Cabernet Sauvignon','Aromas of blackcurrants and cherries with violets and nuances of vanilla oak spice in the background.',NULL,0),(280,1,'Simonsig Cabernet Sauvignon/Merlot','This wine has a vibrant ruby colour and a youthful expression of red berries and luscious cherries, with the attractive sweet notes of chocolate and cinnamon spice. Smooth integrated tannins polish the palate, whilst the dry finish captures the lingering notes of these vibrant fruits.',NULL,0),(281,1,'Simonsig Cabernet Sauvignon/Shiraz','This vibrant, ruby coloured wine shows cheerful notes of red berries layered with luscious plums. A whiff of cinnamon spice contributes to the primary fruit sensation. Youthful yet tame tannins sooth the palate making this wine a true super quaffer.',NULL,0),(282,1,'Tall Horse Cabernet Sauvignon','Rich ruby with layers of ripe forest berry and spice aromas. A gentle smooth entry with delicious ripe berry fruit flavours well married with vanilla oak notes and a smooth juicy finish.',NULL,0),(283,1,'Tilia Cabernet Sauvignon','The nose is full of ripe black fruits with subtle notes of clove, black pepper, and sweet tobacco. On the palate, flavors of black raspberries and cassis yield to more subtle notes of cedar, vanilla, and sweet spice. The fine-grained tannins lend structure to the wine, which has a soft, lingering finish.',NULL,0);
